It also involves building an equivariant neural network for image classification, which falls under the sub-category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper involves the use of artificial intelligence techniques, which could place it under the sub-category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The process of equivarification involves modifying the neural network's architecture, which could also fall under the sub-category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves the use of mathematical concepts such as group theory, which could place it under the sub-category of cs.SD (Systems and Control).
